<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-7242] calling trait method inside closure causes compiler error when CompileStatic is used</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-7242</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Calling f2() within the each closure causes compiler error.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;@groovy.transform.CompileStatic
trait MyTrait {
    def f() {
        [&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;a&apos;&lt;/span&gt;].each {f2()}
    }

    def f2() {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
    }
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
